Item Show page for:<br>
 <h1>Item: <%=@item.name%></h1>
 <li>Year: <%=@item.year%></li>
 <li>Condition: <%=@item.condition%></li>
 <li>Details: <%=@item.detail%></li>
 <li>Item Type: <%=@item.itemtype%></li>
 <li>Quantity: <%=@item.quantity%></li>


Located at:  <%= link_to @item.shop.name, shop_path(@item.shop.id)%><br>
<%= link_to "Edit this item.", edit_shop_item_path(@item.shop, @item)%>

<h2>This item was serviced by a technician on the following dates:</h2>
<%@item.tuneups.each do |tuneup|%>
<li><%=date_format(tuneup.date)%> || By: <%= tuneup.technician.name%></li>
<%end%><br>
